:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c64c61a4378056b3780843346e29e97d230ab5","tid":2084054,"uid":254763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"71維園見"},{"pid":"8e3b1e6f706a781825921fd42281533285441e92","tid":2084054,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">7.1 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DtPsxwh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDtPsxwh.gif&h=37dde5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教大家一個極容易嘅7.1 實體文宣方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2084604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2084604</a>"},{"pid":"2fa87279d953f536dd9bcb32f4b04c6ddad72da7","tid":2084054,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:04:19.000Z","msg":"手足大家71見<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=3ff94395\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"34d9cb69397017dab9502a67380fd5bf3e8ce355","tid":2084054,"uid":104431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"7.1 維園見"},{"pid":"3b88fb36ad907540140cce7f55e197e437aa80a4","tid":2084054,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f307160ef03c6a13e4aa579668d98af9a6ff3aff","tid":2084054,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"叫人衝 自己鬆"},{"pid":"3f22c37d75b44796fe42013ab3e164ec4713eed3","tid":2084054,"uid":114074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b58d94e6c5bf0b6f222ff2c64683b0ac8ba1493","tid":2084054,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:44:51.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"10fe05632d5a2a5091ec0ac82d66cf400d799bf1","tid":2084054,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}